    question: '<h3>How much do you know about HTML text?</h3>\n<p>Write the code to properly express extra importance to key words :</p>\n<pre><code class="language-html">&#x3C;h2>Things To Do&#x3C;/h2>\n&#x3C;ul>\n  &#x3C;li>\n    &#x3C;???>Do Now:&#x3C;???> Call Mum\n  &#x3C;/li>\n  `&#x3C;li>`Buy &#x3C;???>Lord of the Flies&#x3C;???>\n      book`\n   &#x3C;/li>`\n  &#x3C;li>\n    Fix screen on\n    &#x3C;???>iPhone&#x3C;???>\n  &#x3C;/li>\n&#x3C;/ul>\n</code></pre>\n',
